<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA625_06_IH_0001</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema625_06.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_06_ih_0001 paging">
			<section class="title type2 score">
				<h2 data-head="1_light_purple">
					<span lang="y"
						>원을 한없이 잘라서 이어 붙이면 직사각형이 됩니다. 이 직사각형을 이용하여 원의 넓이를 구하는
						방법을 알아보려고 합니다.</span
					>
					<span class="flex align_center"
						><span class="label_bogi">보기</span><span lang="y">를 이용하여 물음에 답해 보세요.</span></span
					>
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents paging_layout">
				<article class="page page_1">
					<h3 class="title">
						<span class="empty_box nemo"></span>
						<span lang="y" class="ml-10">안에 알맞은 말을 써넣으세요.</span>
					</h3>

					<div class="question_box justify_center align_center">
						<div class="dragndrop_fraction_wrap">
							<dl class="bogi_area">
								<dt class="label_bogi" lang="y">보기</dt>
								<dd>
									<ul class="drag_group">
										<li class="drag_item" data-pair="1" data-value="원주">원주</li>
										<li class="drag_item" data-pair="1" data-value="반지름">반지름</li>
										<li class="drag_item" data-pair="1" data-value="지름">지름</li>
										<li class="drag_item" data-pair="1" data-value="원주율">원주율</li>
									</ul>
								</dd>
							</dl>

							<div class="drop_area">
								<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_06_IH/0001_01.png" alt="" />
								<div class="text_area">
									<div class="text1"><span>(</span><span>)</span></div>
									<div class="text2">
										<span>(</span><span>)</span>×
										<div class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>2</span></div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="drop_group">
									<div class="drop_item drop1 hint_up" data-pair="1" data-answer-single="원주"></div>
									<div class="drop_item drop2" data-pair="1" data-answer-single="반지름"></div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p lang="y" class="text_bullet">해설 수급 필요</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- <div class="btn_area">
						<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
						<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
						<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
					</div> -->
				</article>

				<article class="page page_2">
					<h3 class="title">
						<span lang="y"
							>직사각형의 넓이를 구하는 방법을 이용하여 원의 넓이를 구하는 방법을 식으로 나타내려고
							합니다.
						</span>
						<span class="empty_box nemo"></span>
						<span lang="y" class="ml-10">안에 알맞은 말을 </span>
						<span lang="y">써넣으세요.</span>
					</h3>

					<div class="question_box justify_center align_center">
						<div class="dragndrop_fraction_wrap">
							<dl class="bogi_area">
								<dt class="label_bogi" lang="y">보기</dt>
								<dd>
									<ul class="drag_group">
										<li class="drag_item" data-pair="1" data-value="원주">원주</li>
										<li class="drag_item" data-pair="1" data-value="반지름">반지름</li>
										<li class="drag_item" data-pair="1" data-value="지름">지름</li>
										<li class="drag_item" data-pair="1" data-value="원주율">원주율</li>
									</ul>
								</dd>
							</dl>

							<div class="drop_area">
								<div class="text_area">
									<div class="text_row row1">
										<span lang="y">(원의 넓이) =(반지름)×(<span class="blank"></span>)×</span>
										<div class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span> 2 </span></div>
									</div>
									<div class="text_row row2">
										<span lang="y"> (반지름)×(<span class="blank"></span>)×(원주율)× </span>
										<div class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>2</span></div>
										<span lang="y"
											>=( <span class="blank"></span>)×(
											<span class="blank"></span>
											)×(원주율)
										</span>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="drop_group">
									<div class="drop_item drop1 hint_up" data-pair="1" data-answer-single="원주"></div>
									<div class="drop_item drop2 hint_up" data-pair="1" data-answer-single="지름"></div>
									<div
										class="drop_item drop3 hint_up"
										data-pair="1"
										data-answer-single="반지름"
									></div>
									<div
										class="drop_item drop4 hint_up"
										data-pair="1"
										data-answer-single="반지름"
									></div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p lang="y" class="text_bullet">해설 수급 필요</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<div class="btn_area">
					<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
